{"word":"Edomites","slug":"edomites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Edomites</b> Called also Edom.<br/> Descendants of Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36'>Gen 36</a><br/> Kings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=39'>Gen 36:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=14'>Num 20:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=50'>1Ch 1:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=32&verse=29'>Eze 32:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=2&verse=1'>Amo 2:1</a><br/> Dukes of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=43'>Gen 36:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=15'>Exo 15:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=54'>1Ch 1:54</a><br/> Land of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=3'>Gen 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=5'>Deu 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=12'>Deu 2:12</a><br/> Protected by divine command:<br/> - From desolation by the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=6'>Deu 2:6</a> <br/> - From being held in abhorrence by the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=7'>Deu 23:7</a> <br/> Refuse to the Israelites passage through their country<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=21'>Num 20:21</a><br/> Saul makes war against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=47'>1Sa 14:47</a><br/> David:<br/> - Makes conquest of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=16'>1Ki 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=13'>1Ch 18:13</a> <br/> - Installs garrisons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=14'>2Sa 8:14</a> <br/> - Writes battle songs concerning his conquest of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=9'>Psa 60:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=108&verse=10'>Psa 108:10</a> <br/> Become confederates of Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=9'>2Ki 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=26'>2Ki 3:26</a><br/> Ruled by a deputy king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=47'>1Ki 22:47</a><br/> The Lord delivers the army of, into the hands of Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=20'>2Ch 20:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=23'>2Ch 20:23</a><br/> Revolt in the days of Joram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=22'>2Ki 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=10'>2Ch 21:10</a><br/> Amaziah, king of Judah, invades the territory of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=7'>2Ki 14:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=10'>2Ki 14:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=12'>2Ch 25:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=17'>2Ch 28:17</a><br/> Join Babylon in war against the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=35&verse=5'>Eze 35:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=11'>Amo 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=16'>Oba 1:16</a><br/> A Jewish prophet in Babylon denounces<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=137&verse=7'>Psa 137:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=14'>Eze 25:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=35&verse=10'>Eze 35:10</a><br/> Children of the third generation might be received into the congregation of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=8'>Deu 23:8</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=23'>Gen 25:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=29'>Gen 27:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=40'>Gen 27:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=18'>Num 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=11&verse=14'>Isa 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=21&verse=12'>Isa 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=34'>Isa 34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=63&verse=4'>Isa 63:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=9&verse=26'>Jer 9:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=11'>Jer 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=22'>Jer 49:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=22'>Lam 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=14'>Eze 25:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=32&verse=30'>Eze 32:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=35&verse=15'>Eze 35:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=5'>Eze 36:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=19'>Joe 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=12'>Amo 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=9&verse=12'>Amo 9:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&vers